<p rend="chapter">Dhammacakkapavattanadīpanīgāthā</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="174"><hi rend="paranum">174</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Sammāsambodhiñānaṃ hatasakalamalaṃ suddhato cātisuddhaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Addhā laddhā suladdhaṃ vatamiti satataṃ cintayanto subodhiṃ;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Sattāhaṃ sattamevaṃ vividhaphalasukhaṃ vitināmesi kālaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Brahmenāyācito so isipatanavane vattayī dhammacakkaṃ.</p>
